      Font loading strategy:
      - Use preconnect (above) for early connection, not preload (causes crossorigin mismatch warnings)
      - Use font-display=optional to prevent layout shift (fonts only used if loaded in ~100ms)
      - On repeat visits, fonts will be cached and used immediately
